This paper focuses on learning algorithms for robot control, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper specifically compares two learning algorithms, which involves supervised learning (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.AI). The physical robot singulation task also involves image processing (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
